## Rules:
1. Never modify these files unless user explicitly requests changes
2. If components crash, fix the DATA LAYER (hooks), not the components
3. Add fallback data to hooks, never change component structure
4. Test all changes in isolation before applying
5. Always preserve className attributes and styling
